Detailed Description

template<class KEY, class VAL>
class gaia::base::HashMap< KEY, VAL >::iterator

Implements the (non-const) iterator for hashmap. 

 // Creates a hashmap
 HashMap<int, String> hm;
 
 // Adds items for this hashmap.
 if (hmIntStr.size() == 0) {
     for (size_t i = 0; i < 50; i++) {
         hmIntStr.add(i, String::valueOf(i));
     }   
 }
 
 // Creates a hashmap iterator
 HashMap<int, String>::iterator ihm;
 
 // traverse hashmap
 size_t sum = 0;
 for (ihm = hm.begin(); ihm != hm.end(); ihm++) {
            sum += ihm.key();
 }
